科目名稱


計算機網路之隨機分析
Stochastic Analysis of Computer Networks




學分數


3




開課學期


101學年度第二學期




教學目標


The course is intended as an introduction
  to probability theory and stochastic processes. It is particularly well
  suited for those wanting to see how probability theory can be applied to the
  study of computer networks.




教學大綱



Random variables
Conditional probability and
       conditional expectation
Markov chains
The exponential distribution and the
       Poisson process
Continuous-Time Markov chains
Renewal theory and its application
Brownian Motion and Stationary
       Processes (optional)

 




